    "long_instructions": "## Technology\r\n\r\n### AI Contradictions\r\n\r\nAsk AI Chat questions about **automation in modern industries** and notice any places where AI contradicts itself.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Prompt AI Chat by modifying the following question stems. For each prompt, fill in the missing information and then press **Send** one prompt at a time: \r\n \r\n:::details [**Opposite Framing**] \r\n> *Why is it bad/wrong/harmful to...?*\r\n:::\r\n\r\n:::details [**Same Framing**] \r\n>*Why are ... important/beneficial/good?*\r\n:::\r\n\r\n:::details [**Same Framing with a Source (upload a PDF)**] \r\n>*According to the organization ..., why are ... important/beneficial/good?*\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp; \r\n2. Read and compare AI Chat's responses, including its response from the previous level.\r\n3. Note any contradictions and answer the reflection questions in your **Unit Guide**.",
